WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.335 --> 00:00:16.824
Hello, and welcome to Kodland's Tutor Training Program for Roblox Education. This page is designed to give you a clear starting point for your journey into game design with Roblox Studio. Here, you'll begin by selecting your region. It's really important that you choose the correct one.

2
00:00:16.895 --> 00:00:26.515
Because each region has its own training materials, including modules, quizzes, and a file digital skill test that you'll need to complete at the end of your training.

3
00:00:27.075 --> 00:00:31.145
Just to show you an example, I'll go ahead and select the English region.

4
00:00:32.645 --> 00:00:43.054
Once you enter a region, you'll land on the module dashboard. There are 6 modules in total, and you'll need to complete all of them before you can access the digital skill test.

5
00:00:43.235 --> 00:00:47.654
When you're ready, you'll be able to take the DST right after finishing the training.

6
00:00:48.125 --> 00:00:52.335
So, let's open the Module 1 to see what it looks like.

7
00:00:52.575 --> 00:01:02.494
Inside each module, you'll find reading cards, screenshots, and practical examples of what you can actually build inside Roblox Studio.

8
00:01:02.495 --> 00:01:15.875
The goal here isn't to memorize everything. It's to really understand the concepts, so take your time, go through the materials properly, and if possible, try things out directly in Roblox Studio as you learn.

9
00:01:16.295 --> 00:01:21.975
When you feel ready, at the very bottom of the page, you'll find the Take the Quiz button.

10
00:01:22.155 --> 00:01:24.194
This will take you to the module test.

11
00:01:24.395 --> 00:01:29.275
To pass each module, you'll need a score of 70% or higher.

12
00:01:29.585 --> 00:01:37.665
If you don't pass the test on your first try, that's completely fine. You can retake the quiz whenever you feel more ready.

13
00:01:38.295 --> 00:01:42.685
Once you pass, the next module is going to automatically unlock.

14
00:01:44.225 --> 00:02:00.204
If you're already experienced and feel confident with the material, you can also skip the training entirely. At the bottom of the main page, you'll find a button labeled Skip Training and Go Straight to DST, which will take you directly to the digital skill test.

15
00:02:00.985 --> 00:02:12.314
And that's it! We, as Coldan Recruitment Team, wish you the best of luck with your learning journey, and we're really looking forward to seeing your submission in the digital skill test.

